  "detailed_description": "<strong>STORY</strong><br>After an epic multi-day bus trip, Juglio finally arrives in the fallen city of Gettysburg. Days prior he received a mysterious message from his gamer buddy Lenny, instructing him to come over. Juglio now finds himself in an unfamiliar land, searching for clues of Lenny's whereabouts and vowing to do whatever it takes to find his gaming pal.<br><br><strong>GAMEPLAY</strong><br>Explore the open world to find items to help you on your journey to find Lenny. Run, jump, scheme, and sleuth. Most important of all, battle Juglio's greatest enemy -- himself -- in order to achieve success.<br><br><strong>GENRE</strong><br>Open World Comedy Exploration with Unexpected Spooks",
